<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Indro, Jeso velona FFPM125</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Indro, Jeso velona,
 Afaka ny olom-bery,
 Rava re ny fasana,
 Dia nivoaka Ilay Mahery ;
 Ka ny horohorontany
 Dia nahato izany !

[V2]
 Resinao ny rafinay,
 Ry Jesosy manan-kery,
 Ka mpandresy izahay,
 Voavonjinao ny very,
 Matinao ny helok'ota,
 Velona izahay mpanota !</lyrics>
<author>J.R. Ahle</author>
<hymn_number>125</hymn_number>
</song>